# onest Website

Official website for the onest brand (onest.care).

## Project Setup
- Drop your prompt and MD files into the `docs/` folder
- Open this folder in Claude Code to begin development
- Run `npm install` after initial scaffold

## Links
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/onest.care
- Parent company: SV Biotech (https://www.svbiotech.co/th)
